OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FTom Barton reports from Ovingham.
OL,9,FA coroner has described the actions of
OL,10,Fa boy who died trying to save his
OL,11,Ffriend after getting into difficulty
OL,12,Fin the River Tyne as "one of the
OL,13,Fbravest acts that I've ever come
OL,14,Facross".
OL,16,FAras Rudzianskas, 13, drowned in May
OL,17,F2024 in the river at Ovingham, in
OL,18,FNorthumberland, alongside his friend
OL,19,F14-year-old David Radut.
OL,26,@tD@VOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
