OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FThe pair got into difficulties in the
OL,8,Fwater after playing on a rope swing.
OL,10,FOn the second day of an inquest into
OL,11,Fthe boys' deaths in Morpeth on Tuesday
OL,12,F(7 July), Assistant Coroner Paul Dunn
OL,13,Fsaid David's death was an accident.
OL,15,FRecording a narrative conclusion in
OL,16,Frelation to Aras's death, he said he
OL,17,Fhad "selflessly" made "the ultimate
OL,18,Fsacrifice".
OL,26,@yD@EOUyD@PO]yD@WOUzD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FThe coroner also said that
OL,8,F"insufficient action" was taken
OL,9,Fbetween the death of another
OL,10,Fschoolboy, Robert Hattersley, and the
OL,11,Fdeaths of the teenagers on the same
OL,12,Fstretch of water.
OL,14,FThe court heard that safety equipment
OL,15,Fand warning signs were due to be
OL,16,Finstalled following the drowning of 13-
OL,17,Fyear-old Robert, from Crawcrook in
OL,18,FJuly 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FBut despite assurances from
OL,8,FNorthumberland County Council and
OL,9,FNorthumberland Fire Service following
OL,10,FRobert's death, the inquest heard,
OL,11,Fsafety equipment and warning signs had
OL,12,Fnot been installed on the river bank
OL,13,Fby the time David and Aras drowned.
OL,15,FThe coroner heard that permission to
OL,16,Finstall the equipment near where the
OL,17,Fboys entered the water, on land owned
OL,18,Fby Northumberland Estates on the north
OL,19,Fbank of the river, was agreed just
OL,20,Fover a month before they died.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FThe court was also told that emails
OL,8,Fabout the project were sent on the
OL,9,Fmorning before the pair entered the
OL,10,Fwater.
OL,12,FMr Dunn said he would issue a report
OL,13,Fto Prevent Future Deaths (PFD) to
OL,14,FNorthumberland County Council, and the
OL,15,Ffire service which the authority runs,
OL,16,Fas well as Northumberland Estates.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FThe report will state that
OL,8,FNorthumberland County Council, via the
OL,9,Ffire service and their own officers,
OL,10,Fmust maintain a robust multi-agency
OL,11,Fapproach to water safety.
OL,13,FIt will also call for a review of the
OL,14,Fnature of the signage - particularly
OL,15,Fon the north bank of the river - to
OL,16,Finclude reference to the number of
OL,17,Fdeaths there have been in that river
OL,18,Fin a relatively short period of time.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FAnd in respect of Northumberland
OL,8,FEstates, the report will call for the
OL,9,Forganisation to take more direct
OL,10,Fresponsibility as landowners for
OL,11,Fsafety on that stretch of riverbank.
OL,13,FOn Monday, Detective Sergeant Danielle
OL,14,FGrant, of Northumbria Police, told the
OL,15,Finquest that witnesses suggested the
OL,16,Ftwo boys started swinging on a rope
OL,17,Fswing over the river and back again,
OL,18,Fshortly after arriving at the river on
OL,19,F18 May 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FThe court was told they did this twice
OL,8,Fsuccessfully, but, according to
OL,9,Fwitnesses, on David's second attempt
OL,10,Fhe let go of the rope and fell into
OL,11,Fdeeper water, struggling because he
OL,12,Fcould not swim.
OL,14,FWitnesses said Aras went into the
OL,15,Fwater to rescue David, but was pulled
OL,16,Fdown as David panicked.
OL,18,FThe court heard two other boys
OL,19,Fattempted to help, but David
OL,20,Fdisappeared under the water and Aras
OL,21,Fwas taken by the current.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FDavid was found downstream and was
OL,8,Fdeclared dead at the scene. Aras died
OL,9,Fin hospital three days later.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FThe court heard on Tuesday that David
OL,17,Fwas not a swimmer but he did not need
OL,18,Fto be for the activity he was engaging
OL,19,Fin.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FThe coroner said he got into
OL,8,Fdifficulties as a result of an
OL,9,Faccident and did not mean to fall into
OL,10,Fthe river, having already successfully
OL,11,Fswung one or two times.
OL,13,FOf Aras, Mr Dunn said if there was a
OL,14,Fshort form conclusion for bravery, he
OL,15,Fwould have recorded it for him.
OL,17,FHe said: "His courage to go in was one
OL,18,Fof the bravest acts that I've ever
OL,19,Fcome across in my 20 years as a
OL,20,Fcoroner."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1783707575
OL,3,CCoroner says boy's efforts to save
OL,4,Cdrowning friend was 'one of bravest
OL,5,Cacts'
OL,7,FRecording a narrative conclusion, he
OL,8,Fsaid Aras died as a result of the
OL,9,Feffects of drowning while attempting
OL,10,Fto save the life of his friend in the
OL,11,FRiver Tyne at Ovingham.
OL,13,FMr Dunn added that "he gave the
OL,14,Fultimate sacrifice selflessly" in
OL,15,Ftrying to save David.
OL,17,FThe coroner also praised other
OL,18,Fchildren who were there, describing
OL,19,Ftheir reaction to such a "dreadful
OL,20,Fexperience" as the kind expected of
OL,21,F"decent kids".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
